data.description: This 4-room, 2-bath home starred in Season 12 Ep 5 of the hit show Texas Flip n Move! TV-worthy renovations! This wildly televised abode spans an expansive 1,985 sq. ft. footprint, occupying a generous 1-acre plot that provides an idyllic setting for outdoor gatherings and leisure. Marvel at the lofty ceilings, the seamless flow of the open floorplan, and the abundant natural light that hits every corner of this well-maintained home, accentuating the allure of the exquisite wood laminate flooring and granite countertops. The kitchen is a haven for culinary enthusiasts, featuring SS appliances and ample cabinetry for storage convenience. Unwind in the master suite, which includes a TX sized walk-in clst, dual sinks, tub and a walk-in shower. The 3 additional bedrooms are generously proportioned and have the same enchanting wood laminate flooring. Adding to the allure, a substantial 48 X 30 barn stands ready for transformation into a garage, and offering ample space for parking.
